This PR adds support for https://huggingface.co/hexgrad/Kokoro-82M, and adds the `RawAudio` class (PR extended from #682).

Example code coming soon.

The docs for this PR live [here](https://moon-ci-docs.huggingface.co/docs/transformers.js/pr_1148). All of your documentation changes will be reflected on that endpoint. The docs are available until 30 days after the last update.
